      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $0 < a_1 < a_2 < \\dots < a_p$ des réels fixés.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(0 &lt; a_1 &lt; a_2 &lt; \\dots\n&lt; a_p\\)</span> des réels fixés.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8b9541cc-af34-4126-adde-c697e07b47cd",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que pour tout réel $a > a_p$ il existe un unique réel $x_a > 0$\n      solution de l'équation : $a_1^x + \\dots + a_p^x = a^x$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que pour tout réel <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a &gt;\na_p\\)</span> il existe un unique réel <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_a\n&gt; 0\\)</span> solution de l’équation : <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(a_1^x + \\dots + a_p^x = a^x\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "aa2a221a-3285-49ab-84db-e443b088203c",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "\\'Etude de $x \\mapsto \\left(\\frac{a_1}a\\right)^x + \\dots + \\left(\\frac{a_p}a\\right)^x$.",
        "html": "<p>Étude de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x \\mapsto\n\\left(\\frac{a_1}a\\right)^x + \\dots +\n\\left(\\frac{a_p}a\\right)^x\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6a97c774-efcd-4992-a8a1-2077c3b446a5",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Pour $a < b$, comparer $x_a$ et $x_b$.",
        "html": "<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a &lt; b\\)</span>, comparer <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(x_a\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(x_b\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4420a667-2bf1-463c-95f4-fb2ab8c68222",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$x_a > x_b$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_a &gt; x_b\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f6b29718-906a-4981-83c2-530ea10c06da",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Chercher $\\lim_{a\\to+\\infty} x_a$ puis\n      $\\lim_{a\\to+\\infty} x_a\\ln a$",
        "html": "<p>Chercher <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim_{a\\to+\\infty} x_a\\)</span>\npuis <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim_{a\\to+\\infty} x_a\\ln\na\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "fe02806e-5149-4fb7-960e-8c254140ec71",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$x_a\\to\\ell$.\n               Si $\\ell > 0$, $a^{a_a} \\to +\\infty$, mais\n               $a_1^{x_a} + \\dots + a_p^{x_a} \\to a_1^\\ell + \\dots + a_p^\\ell$.\n\n               Donc $\\ell = 0$, et $x_a\\ln a \\to \\ln p$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_a\\to\\ell\\)</span>. Si <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\ell &gt; 0\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(a^{a_a} \\to +\\infty\\)</span>, mais <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(a_1^{x_a} + \\dots + a_p^{x_a} \\to a_1^\\ell + \\dots\n+ a_p^\\ell\\)</span>.</p>\n<p>Donc <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\ell = 0\\)</span>, et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(x_a\\ln a \\to \\ln p\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
